yN_HQ5vm7nk.title: Betty's Salted Caramel Pudding
yN_HQ5vm7nk.description:
Betty demonstrates how to make Salted Caramel Pudding.  This pudding has a delicious flavor and a light, airy texture.

Salted Caramel Pudding

┬╛ cup light brown sugar, firmly packed
1 ounce light cream or half-and-half
1 tablespoon butter
┬╜ teaspoon vanilla extract
1 ┬╜ tablespoons cornstarch
1 ┬╜ tablespoons flour
1 ┬╜ tablespoons white sugar
2 ┬╜ ounces additional milk
2 eggs
1 quart additional milk
1/8 teaspoon coarse sea salt
1 cup whipped topping (Cool Whip)
additional sea salt for topping

In a small saucepan, make a caramel mixture as follows:  Bring brown sugar, light cream, butter, and vanilla to a boil over low to medium heat.  Without stirring, boil over low heat for about 8 minutes.  Set aside to cool.  In a large bowl, mix cornstarch, flour, and sugar.  Add 2 ┬╜ ounces milk very slowly, stirring until mixture is smooth.  Add eggs and beat well with a mixer on medium speed.  Heat 1 quart milk in a medium saucepan until hot, but not boiling.  Add a small amount of the hot mixture to the beaten egg mixture and then pour the egg mixture into the hot milk, stirring well.  Stir in about 1/8 teaspoon coarse sea salt.  Set aside to cool for about 15 minutes.  Stir in the caramel mixture.  Place on stove and cook over medium heat, stirring often, until mixture is thick and bubbly.  Cool at room temperature for about an hour.  Then, refrigerate for at least 4 hours, stirring occasionally while cooling, until mixture is of pudding consistency.  Fold in whipped topping, cover with plastic wrap, and refrigerate until ready to serve.  To serve, spoon pudding into sherbet glasses.  Sprinkle top of each with a small amount of coarse sea salt.  Enjoy!  I hope you love this recipe!  --  Betty  тЩе

QlL0rwOcLIE.title: Rocksmith - Boston - More Than A Feeling (Combo)
QlL0rwOcLIE.description:
It seems like no-one records Combo 1 for this song. It's the better of the two arrangements,in my opinion, so I threw up a run of my own. The two solos are in Combo 2, meaning they ARE NOT in this video.

This is probably my proudest Rocksmith achievement so far. I set a goal in July to get this arrangement 100% leveled and to play it pretty well. I think I've accomplished that but some of my transitions could use a bit more practice. Moving to that Bm chord gives me a bit of trouble too. 

I'd say this song is my favorite in RS so far. Combo 2 has the solos in it (which is probably why its more popular to record) but I think this one is funner and sounds better. This arrangement is definitely the harder of the two and it took quite a bit of practice in Riff Repeater to get everything close to memorized.

I am NOT using the default tone (Mass Drive) for this song. There are several songs in RS that sound terrible with the default tone and this is one of them. There's WAY too much distortion in it for my tastes so I made a custom one: Bahston. The chorus ( I think that's what it's called, starts at 0:39) sounds a little meh with mine but it's too much of a hassle to try and change tones during the song.

Kinda wish I had a way to get a "Hand Cam" thing going. Sort of like what Elison and some other RS recorders have done. That probably would have been neat for this one.

Miele is a German manufacturer and global leader in premium domestic appliances and commercial equipment. It is committed to reliability and durability, combining advanced technology with superior quality. All Miele domestic appliances are tested for the equivalent of 20 years use*.
Founded in 1899, Miele has always been a family-owned, family-run company, belonging to the Miele and Zinkann families – today each in their fourth generation.  The company motto of Immer Besser, meaning Forever Better, underpins every Miele endeavour; it drives innovation through the passion for finding better ways of doing things, and a desire to enrich people’s lives and bring pleasure to every household. The product range includes household appliances for laundry, cooking, refrigeration, dishwashing and vacuums, and commercial appliances for laundry, sterilisation and dishwashing.
Miele encourages its UK customers to come and test the products before they make a purchase at the Experience Centres in Abingdon, Oxfordshire or London. Miele has also developed Taste for Design; a range of exciting cooking courses, demonstrations and appliance schools in London and Abingdon. Courses are available for pre-purchase and owners as well as food classes for lovers of great food and cooking.
Miele is proud to have been crowned Home Appliance Brand of the Year at the prestigious Which? Awards for a second consecutive year (2015/2016), as well as the supplier of appliances for a wide range of quality hospitals, hotels, restaurants, sport facilities and prestigious residences across the UK and worldwide including The All England Lawn Tennis Club at Wimbledon, Italy’s Grand Hotel A Villa Feltrinelli, Vienna’s Hofburg Imperial Palace and The Kremlin.
For further information please visit www.miele.co.uk

Xu3-PmKFVag.title: Sworn Brothers | Zelda: Ocarina of Time 100% Walkthrough "16/89" (No Commentary)
Xu3-PmKFVag.description:
We are met by Darunia and awarded the Goron's Ruby for clearing out Dodongo's Cavern. We head downhill a little and blow up a boulder in the wall to get Gold Skulltula #18 . We then use our bugs on the soft soil patch at the entrance to Dodongo's Cavern for Gold Skulltula #19 . We then enter Goron City and use a bomb to stop Hot Rodder Goron (near his sign in the dark spot) for the Big Bomb Bag upgrade. Lastly at the top of Goron City we blow a path through the boulder maze with bombs to get Gold Skulltula #20 and a ton of rupees before leaving Goron City.

Collectibles: 5

1. Goron's Ruby - 1:30 (One of the 3 Sacred Stones)
2. Gold Skulltula #18 of 100 - 2:52 (Death Mountain Trail, behind a bomb-able wall, can be reached via climbing up the wall)
3. Gold Skulltula #19 of 100 - 3:40 (Death Mountain Trail, Soft Soil spot, use a bug to flush it out)
4. Big Bomb Bag - 5:18 (Goron City, bomb Hot Rodder Goron under the archway, Medium Bomb Bag Upgrade, holds 30 Bombs)
5. Gold Skulltula #20 of 100 - 6:54 (Goron City, in the rock maze, inside a crate)

_UbSIIUpaBg.title: Star Ocean 3 Music Soundtracks - The Incarnation of Devil
_UbSIIUpaBg.description:
The music for this game was composed by Motoi Sakuraba, a long-time collaborator with tri-Ace. The soundtrack was eventually released in four parts:

* Original Soundtrack Volume 1 - A 2-CD set containing mainly the softer and orchestral pieces from the game.
* Original Soundtrack Volume 2 - Another 2-CD set containing the upbeat music, primarily the battle and dungeon themes.
* Arrange Album - A selection of tracks from the game reworked in different styles.
* Voice Mix - Similar to the Arrange Album, but featuring dialogue sampled from the Japanese version of the game along with the music.

The limited edition of Volume 1 also came with a box to hold all four albums.

When the game was revised into the Director's Cut, Sakuraba composed a few new pieces of music and released an album for them.

The song "The Small Bird That Forgot How To Fly", Tobikata Wo Wasureta Chiisana Tori) by the JPop singer MISIA was used to accompany the game's ending credits.

Cn8lZH7fFc8.title: Imparare a sciare con Girovagando in Valle di Fiemme
Cn8lZH7fFc8.description: Intense da quest'anno anche le sciate sotto le stelle sulle piste perfettamente illuminate del Cermis e di Pampeago. Presso lo Ski center Latemar le piste sono aperte il martedì, il giovedì e il venerdì. All'alpe Cermis il mercoledì, il venerdì e la domenica. L'orario è sempre dalle 19:30 alle 22:30. Il fascino dello sci alpino in Val di Fiemme si traduce in 100 km di piste, 120 maestri di sci, 50 dei più moderni impianti di risalita e un servizio gratuito di skibus. Con un unico skipass é possibile sciare ogni giorno in un area sciistica diversa nel comprensorio della valle o del Dolomiti superski con i suoi 1220 chilometri di piste e 460 impianti di risalita. Tutte le aree prestano particolare attenzione alle esigenze dei piccoli sciatori, che vogliono imparare a sciare divertendosi e giocando, per questo sono attrezzate con colorati Kindergarten, snow park e campi scuola per principianti.

BNyLCETJ5R8.title: Alice nel paese delle meraviglie: il signor serratura
BNyLCETJ5R8.description:
LEGGERE PRIMA DI GUARDARE

Il signor Serratura è l'unico personaggio del film Disney a non essere stato preso dai libri; egli non appare nè in "Alice underground" (la prima versione di "Alice nel paese delle meraviglie"), nè in "Alice nel paese delle meraviglie", nè in "Attraverso lo specchio e quel che Alice vi trovò". Questo personaggio è stato inventato dagli autori Disney e inserito nella storia (per ragioni a me completamente oscure); anche tutte le sue battute e i suoi giochi di parole sono stati completamente inventati.

Il video che ho fatto è molto semplice: ho messo la versine italiana del film seguita da quella inglese (da notare l'enorme differenza della traduzione).

I clip sono del film Disney "Alice nel paese delle meraviglie" (tutti i diritti riservati)

La musica iniziale fa parte del soundtrack di Coraline e la porta magica senza voler violare i copyright della Focus Features, della LAIKA, e di Bruno Coulais il grande compositore.

BNxUQRTMhDk.title: Privacy settings tutorial for xbox 360; including how to block friend's list after kinect update
BNxUQRTMhDk.description:
I describe how to change your privacy settings that were known to be under your profile button on the xbox guide settings tab. They moved it since the last dashboard update. I also describe what most of them do, which are divided into 4 categories; Activity, Privacy, Content, and Contact preferences. 
The first two under activity are  "Voice and text," and "Video communication". The next 7 (best ones) under privacy are Profile Sharing, Kinect Sharing, Game History, Online Status, Video and Music Status, Friends List, and Voice Data Collection. The next 4 under content are Programming, Profile Viewing, Member Content, and the notoriously famous Explicit Content (:D). The last 2 under Contact Preferences are Xbox Marketing and Partner Marketing. Subscribe please. Thank you
